      "path": "audio/narrations/number-bases/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 28080,
      "text": "我们从小数数，都是十个一数，满十就进一位。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "number-bases",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/number-bases/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 27936,
      "text": "为什么是十？也许只因为我们有十根手指。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "number-bases",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/number-bases/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.1,
      "size": 33552,
      "text": "数字 365，其实是三个一百、六个十、加五个一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "number-bases",
      "section_id": "placevalue",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "placevalue-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/number-bases/xiaoxiao/placevalue-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.76,
      "size": 28224,
      "text": "这就是位值制：每一位的权重，是进制的一个幂。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "number-bases",
      "section_id": "placevalue",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "placevalue-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/number-bases/xiaoxiao/placevalue-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 3.1,
      "size": 49680,
      "text": "十进制里，从右往左依次是一、十、百、千，也就是十的零次、一次、二次方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "number-bases",
      "section_id": "placevalue",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "placevalue-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/number-bases/xiaoxiao/placevalue-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "换一个进制，规则不变，只是把底数从十换成别的数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "number-bases",
      "section_id": "binary",
      "line_id": "bin-1",
      "filename": "binary-bin-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/number-bases/xiaoxiao/binary-bin-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.25,
      "size": 36000,
      "text": "计算机只认两种状态，开与关，于是用二进制，逢二进一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "number-bases",
      "section_id": "binary",
      "line_id": "bin-2",
      "filename": "binary-bin-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/number-bases/xiaoxiao/binary-bin-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.43,
      "size": 38880,
      "text": "每一位只有零和一，权重是二的幂：一、二、四、八、十六。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "number-bases",
      "section_id": "binary",
      "line_id": "bin-3",
      "filename": "binary-bin-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/number-bases/xiaoxiao/binary-bin-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.27,
      "size": 36288,
      "text": "比如 1101，就是八加四加一，正好等于十进制的十三。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "number-bases",
      "section_id": "hex",
      "line_id": "hex-1",
      "filename": "hex-hex-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/number-bases/xiaoxiao/hex-hex-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.65,
      "size": 26352,
      "text": "二进制太长，于是人们用十六进制来压缩它。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "number-bases",
      "section_id": "hex",
      "line_id": "hex-2",
      "filename": "hex-hex-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/number-bases/xiaoxiao/hex-hex-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "每四个二进制位，正好对应一个十六进制符号，从零到 F。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "number-bases",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/number-bases/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "输入一个数字，看它在二、八、十、十六进制下如何展开。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "number-bases",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/number-bases/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.5,
      "size": 24048,
      "text": "注意同一个数，进制越小，位数就越多。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "number-bases",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/number-bases/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "进制只是选择一个底数，位值制的规则始终如一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "number-bases",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/number-bases/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "每一位的权重都是底数的幂，各位相加就还原出原数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "number-bases",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/number-bases/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "理解了位值，你就读懂了机器的语言，我们下次再见！"
